      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:26:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦为拜登辩护，称其在会议中“极其高效”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在众议院听证会上，当被问及总统的精神敏锐度时，财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，她的老板乔·拜登在他们都参加的长时间会议中表现得“极其高效”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/yellen-defends-biden-as-extremely-effective-in-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 16:11:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>RTX 即将与 Arcline 达成协议出售其子公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/rtx-corp-is-said-to-near-deal-to-sell-unit-to-arcline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，RTX 公司正就将其柯林斯航空航天部门的一个部门出售给私募股权公司 Arcline Investment Management 进行深入谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/rtx-corp-is-said-to-near-deal-to-sell-unit-to-arcline</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:54:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Puig 将加入西班牙基准股票指数，Melia 将退出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/puig-to-join-spain-s-benchmark-stock-index-melia-set-for-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奢侈美容公司 Puig Brands SA 将被纳入西班牙基准股票指数，取代 Melia Hotels International SA，这是该蓝筹股指数一年半以来的首次调整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/puig-to-join-spain-s-benchmark-stock-index-melia-set-for-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 15:52:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Bobby Jain 的复杂对冲基金首次亮相，引来众多粉丝和质疑者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/bobby-jain-s-complex-hedge-fund-debut-spawns-fans-and-doubters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在优雅的 Breakers Palm Beach 度假村内，Bobby Jain 进行了价值数十亿美元的宣传。他的听众是阿布扎比投资局，该局掌管着全球最大的石油公司之一，对 Jain 来说，他是他的新对冲基金的完美客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/bobby-jain-s-complex-hedge-fund-debut-spawns-fans-and-doubters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁风险导致俄罗斯接受人民币步伐放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/russia-s-embrace-of-chinese-yuan-stalls-over-risk-from-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受俄罗斯入侵乌克兰与西方国家关系紧张的影响，俄罗斯总统普京的战时经济中人民币的快速增长或许已经达到极限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/russia-s-embrace-of-chinese-yuan-stalls-over-risk-from-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 06:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国现在必须面对它宁愿忽视的债券市场风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-election-shock-alerts-bond-market-investors-to-fiscal-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国的政治冲击迫使债券投资者面对现实：该国的财政赤字是当前的问题，而不是未来几年的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-s-election-shock-alerts-bond-market-investors-to-fiscal-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：鲍威尔“平衡”基调推动股市维持高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于华尔街认为杰罗姆鲍威尔的经济言论是平衡的，股市徘徊在历史高位附近，这加强了人们对美联储今年将能够降息的猜测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 22:32:57 GMT</pubDate>
